external.gw.api.address

Interface AddressOwner

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ABContactPrimaryAddressOwner, AbstractAddressOwner, AddressOwnerBase, ContactPrimaryAddressOwner, SearchAddressOwner, SearchProximityAddressOwner, SecondaryAddressOwner
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface AddressOwner
    Interface for a helper object passed to the standard Address input set. The helper object provides a way to set/get a single address on the enclosing entity (for example to set and get the primary address for a Contact). It also contains information about which fields should be visible, required etc.
